        <mxCell id="c5_what" value="•  Joins outputs from Extraction + Policy + Validation&#10;•  Structured prompt  ·  apply coverage to facts&#10;•  Calculates payout  (loss − deductible, capped at limit)&#10;•  Reasons about fraud signals + edge cases&#10;•  Self-rates its confidence on a 0 – 1 scale&#10;•  Recommends tier  (T1 auto · T2 adjuster · T3 CSR)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=13;fontColor=#0a2540;spacingTop=4" vertex="1" parent="1">
